Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:24.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh? Orang itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:28.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Punggungnya terlihat agak familier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh ya, dari pencarian internet barusan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kuduga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang itu selalu muncul\Ndi foto lokasi kejadian penjahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi, dia mungkin tahu sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:45.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tuh, dia kabur! Mencurigakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi, kejar juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:51.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Eh?\NTu-Tunggu dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya periksa lidahnya dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:05.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau akan membayar soal kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:17.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah selesai, nih?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:25.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, sepertinya\Nada kesalahpahaman di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:29.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena ini tidak tergolong\Npenggunaan Quirk ilegal,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:32.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tidak punya alasan untuk menangkapmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:41.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kupikir kau semacam penjahat tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:44.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sering dikira begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya. Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:50.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berani-beraninya dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa menuntutnya\Ndengan apa pun di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:58.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Erasure tidak berfungsi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:04:59.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu berarti,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia Quirkless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma pria tua yang badannya kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tetap saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia orang mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minimal aku laporkan ke polisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penjahat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada penjahat muncul!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:27.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masih jago kabur kayak biasa, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Coba hindari yang ini juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sini juga ada aku, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan pada saat yang sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:05.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Guru... Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gadis itu ke mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia lagi mengejar pekerja kantoran tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bakal kubiarkan kabur!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:21.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Apa ini?!\NAku tidak bisa gerak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menghadapi orang sepertimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah pekerjaan seorang pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski hari ini aku sedang libur.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bilang tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:54.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bonekaku lagi-lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:07:00.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bonekaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gede banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu penjahat raksasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:52.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kabur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gila!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Foto, foto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:56.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bodoh! Panggil pahlawan, lah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:08:01.79,tanda-5,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\bord3\fad(400,0)\b1\c&H211B12&\3c&HF8EB9C&\pos(1485,794)}Quirk "Mainan Aksi"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:27.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gu-Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Quirk dia adalah Lompatan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia tidak punya pijakan buat melompat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:43.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begini terus,\Ndia bakal jatuh menghantam tanah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:53.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau menemaninya\Nmelakukan hal seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:56.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,bertanya itu padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan jawabannya adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku ingin jadi pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan pernah bisa\Njadi pahlawan profesional sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu itu, tapi tetap saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau cuma sesaat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ingin terbang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke! Lompat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selamat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:56.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia datang lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:17.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau Quirk pembesaran dihapus,\Njelas dia akan menyusut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:22.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menangkapnya setelah itu adalah\Nlangkah yang paling logis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:34.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah... bagaimanapun juga,\Nterima kasih atas bantuannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:38.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang, aku juga\Nseorang warga sipil yang baik hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:41.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membantu pahlawan itu kewajiban yang wajar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permainan pura-pura jadi pahlawan kalian
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:46.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,terlalu berbahaya\Nuntuk disebut sebagai niat baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:51.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami melakukan hal-hal yang tidak bisa\Ndilakukan oleh pahlawan profesional.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hal yang tidak bisa dilakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:58.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti penjahat raksasa\Ndan preman kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:01.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami bisa mengalahkan mereka\Nsebelum mereka sempat berbuat jahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memukul orang\Nsebelum mereka berbuat apa-apa,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:07.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu juga kejahatan, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:09.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau pakai logika itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:14.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami baru bisa dituntut\Nsetelah melakukan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:18.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi kau sengaja melakukan kejahatan\Nkarena kau mendapat hasil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:21.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar-benar\Norang tua yang bermasalah, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:23.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sudah sering kudengar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:30.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kouichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, cuma agak capek saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:38.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya aku tidak mencoba hal\Nyang tidak biasa kulakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:41.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berlagak kayak pahlawan\Ndan bikin aksi heboh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang bukan gayaku, sih,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan ujung-ujungnya malah jatuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:49.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kupikir aku bakal mati tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:53.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengar, ya,\Nomongan kayak begitu tuh, nye-be-lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ngapain sih, pakai alasan-alasan begitu?\NMerendah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:00.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada gunanya, mending hentikan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadinya aku mau bilang "terima kasih",
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:06.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi karena kau nyebelin, batal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:11.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,mau tahu kenapa kau jatuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena kau terbang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:18.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tinggal masalah mendaratnya saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:22.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau jatuh ke tempat sampah\Nsama kayak aku, itu bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:26.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi masih banyak hal lain\Nyang harus kau pelajari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:29.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, sudah kubilang, aku bukan muridmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Api tadi kau memanggilku guru, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, itu hanya tidak sengaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya Knuckle itu susah disebut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Justru karena tidak sengaja itulah penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kata atau tindakan\Nyang muncul secara spontan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu yang mencerminkan\Nisi hatimu sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima saja, calon pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:56.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, bukankah logika itu... agak memaksa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:08.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, benar, hanya perkelahian biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa masalahmu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau sok-sokan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan remehkan aku, dasar kampungan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katakan langsung padaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:17.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan jangan telan ludahmu sendiri,\Ndasar pecundang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka menggunakan Quirk\Ndan mengamuk di depan stasiun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:27.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya mereka anak SMA,\Ndilihat dari seragam mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:30.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau dari SMP mana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sendiri dari SMP mana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, maaf. Ternyata anak SMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, aku akan segera ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:38.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:41.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku punya sesuatu yang bagus buatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:41.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesuatu yang bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sarung tangan pelindung\Nuntuk pengendara motor,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan pelindung tubuh untuk dipakai\Ndi bawah hoodie-mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan ini kau bisa ngebut\Nsemaksimal mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:55.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan, kalian berdua!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan kau?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baik-baik saja?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama sekali tidak sakit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:10.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa-apaan kau tiba-tiba muncul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maju sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:17.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau pakai nama "Nice Guy",\Nkau bakal diremehkan penjahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:20.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau butuh nama baru juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:37.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria dengan aroma penuh misteri...\NThe Crawler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:40.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Ngomong apa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau kan Nice Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:46.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, kau itu yang suka pungut sampah, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keren juga kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan, sekarang bukan Nice Guy lagi,\Ntapi The Crawler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,The Howler?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, tidak!\NBukan The Howler, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,The Crawler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gaya ngomong berlidah itu\Nngeselin banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pokoknya, hentikan perkelahian ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekerasan itu tidak baik, oke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:08.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah?!\NSiapa yang suruh kau ngatur-ngatur?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:11.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan?\NBerhenti, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada pelindungnya, jadi tidak sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurang ajar kau, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mataku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan sok keren kau, Nice Guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,The Crawler!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mendingan kau\Npungut sampah saja kayak biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:29.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau soal bersih-bersih, aku bisa bantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:36.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membersihkan sampah seperti kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:37.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Guru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa paman ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:43.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak-anak bodoh,\Nsekarang aku akan menghajar kalian!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:46.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah itu ada yang mau kupastikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak perlu dihajar juga, 'kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:51.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa sih, selalu mulai dari situ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya lebih cepat dan pasti\Nkalau dihajar dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, rasanya memuaskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:58.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menghajar orang\Ndemi rasa puas itu tidak boleh, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa tidak?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:03.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian ngomong apa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Uh, ini semua berantakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:12.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hai! Boleh ganggu sebentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:13.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,PopāStep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:16.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku selalu nonton videomu di internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Aku juga selalu klik suka, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih!\NMau tanda tangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:22.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mohon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:27.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang-orang ini, sih...\Nsebenarnya tidak jahat,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:29.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi juga tidak sepenuhnya waras.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku waras, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:32.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau yakin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penjahat! Ada penjahat muncul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:42.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keras! Aku sangat keras!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:46.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak terkalahkan!\NLebih keras dari gedung pencakar langit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah! Bayi itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penyelamatan berhasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:09.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, itu terlihat gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Panggil pahlawan! Cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:15.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada yang bisa melukaiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:17.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Guru, lihat itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, sepertinya kita tepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita beraksi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:27.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Betapa kuatnya penjahat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:32.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu karena obat berbahaya bernama Trigger\Nyang bisa ubah orang biasa jadi penjahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:39.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka itu sukarelawan yang berusaha\Nmenghentikan peredarannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:43.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ini manusia super!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:48.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang-orang biasa sepertimu, cuma lari-lari\Ndi kakiku tak ada gunanya sama sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selagi dia teralihkan perhatiannya olehku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:58.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian para penjahat dadakan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,belum terbiasa dengan kekuatan Quirk kalian\Nyang lepas kendali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian penuh celah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Misalnya, kau terlalu mengeraskan tubuhmu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,dengan Quirk pengerasan\Nsampai gerakanmu jadi lambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:11.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sebabnya kau gampang jatuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:15.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan karena pengerasan kalian\Nbersifat sadar, bukan mutasi alami,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau kau kehilangan fokus,\Ntubuhmu akan melemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu kena satu pukulan, sisanya gampang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak akan kuberi kesempatan untuk pulih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makanya, jangan sok hebat\Ncuma karena pakai pengerasan, dasar bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh, kau terlalu berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:40.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, dia pingsan\Ndan kekuatan pengerasannya mulai hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita ambil foto buat identifikasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:49.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mukanya... tidak kelihatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:52.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya kau kebanyakan memukulnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh, aku berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah kau selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:02.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau kita ambil foto lagi,\Nbuat jaga-jaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:07.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:09.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,jangan lupa ambil fotonya\Nsambil menunjukkan lidah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lidah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:14.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang yang pakai Trigger\Nlidahnya berubah warna jadi hitam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tanda khasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:21.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian juga hati-hati, cek teman kalian,\Njangan sampai ada yang ikut-ikutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:23.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau ada apa-apa, kirim aku surel, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, obat itu memang tidak baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:28.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, barang itu berbahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Polisi datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke, kita kabur!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, sampai ketemu lagi, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:42.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Datang ke konserku juga, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian ini siapa sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:50.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami adalah pahlawan misterius baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Knuckleduster dan The Crawler!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:02.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Identitas tersangka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:05.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada dalam daftar penjahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:09.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang sedang dicocokkan\Ndengan pendaftaran Quirk umum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Polisi lokal bilang,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,tersangka punya Quirk pengerasan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,kekuatan super, dan kemampuan membesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tipe yang cukup mencolok, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, kemungkinan cepat ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soalnya Quirk gabungan jarang ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:27.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, mungkin kita tidak akan bisa\Ntemukan di daftar resmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:34.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perubahan warna di mulut\Nakibat gangguan aliran darah,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,faktor Quirk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:39.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,efek samping dari konsumsi Idio-Trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:42.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,istilahnya, penjahat dadakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:45.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi wajahnya parah banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:48.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa pahlawan yang menangani ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa-bisa dapat suspensi\Nkarena tindakan berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:56.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada kesaksian kalau sepasang pahlawan\Nyang bertarung,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:21:00.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi tidak ada laporan\Npengiriman pahlawan resmi ke daerah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:02.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:05.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama seperti kejadian penjahat raksasa\Nbeberapa waktu lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pahlawan ilegal tanpa izin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:12.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Alias Vigilante.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:15.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, siapa pun mereka,\Nselama mereka mengalahkan penjahat,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:16.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,hasil akhirnya tetap bagus, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:19.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Sansa,\Njangan asal ngomong begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada hukum yang berlaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:26.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun musuhnya penjahat,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:30.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,tindakan main hakim sendiri itu\Ntetap pelanggaran hukum.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:36.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kejadian hari ini\Nsudah jadi bahan gosip, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana tanggapan tentang pahlawan baru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:42.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua orang menyebut kalian,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:45.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Paman Tinju Monster",
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:47.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan "The Howler".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:51.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,The Crawler!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:55.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namaku itu The Crawler!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:29.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meskipun aku memulai aktivitas pahlawan\Nsecara ilegal,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:31.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku hanyalah seorang mahasiswa biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:33.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau lebih tepatnya,\Nmahasiswa yang kesepian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:36.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi ada beberapa situasi\Nyang bisa ditemukan karena aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:38.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya, "Lebah".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, menurutku itu hal yang baik.
